#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:7
msgid "Learn how to process images and audio with LLMs."
msgstr "LLMを使用して画像と音声を処理する方法を学びます。"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:11
msgid "Vision"
msgstr "ビジョン"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/multimodal.rst:13
msgid ""
"With the ``vision`` ability you can have your model take in images and "
"answer questions about them. Within Xinference, this indicates that certain "
"models are capable of processing image inputs when conducting dialogues via "
"the Chat API."
msgstr ""
"``vision``機能により、モデルは画像を受け取り、それに関する質問に回答できます。Xinferenceでは、これは特定のモデルがChat "
"APIを通じた対話時に画像入力を処理できることを意味します。"

